content:
Enable Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator for Your Org

To enable Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator to work in your org and select the user license, do the following:

Where: This feature is available in Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

How: From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator Settings and select it.
title: Enable Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator for Salesforce
